"{\"uid\": \"globalnews.ca-news-10278931-olympic-village-vancouver-no-school\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Instructions:  Want to discuss?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 31, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please read ourCommenting Policyfirst.\", \"from\": 32, \"to\": 70, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you get Global News from Instagram or Facebook - that will be changing.Find out how you can still connect with us.\", \"from\": 72, \"to\": 189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 83, \"end\": 94, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Global_News\", \"score\": 0.99998270601934, \"rank\": 1.7294279803571782e-05, \"text\": \"Global News\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Global_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Global_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more than 15 years there is been talk of building a school in Vancouver'sOlympic Village, yet the barren piece of land set aside for the elementary school remains undeveloped.\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 257, \"end\": 266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 0.9999999489068627, \"rank\": 5.109316941729773e-08, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wish it had been built 15 years ago when it was supposed to have been built,\\\" nearby resident Alex Oulton said.\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 469, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.9999937969877494, \"rank\": 6.179730078996631e-06, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}, {\"begin\": 474, \"end\": 480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oulton_Park\", \"score\": 0.9999999920544269, \"rank\": 7.936912838808665e-09, \"text\": \"Oulton\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oulton_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oulton_Park\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2007, the development plan for Olympic Village anticipated an elementary school for the neighbourhood.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 522, \"end\": 537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9923634111515969, \"rank\": 0.007694161957511591, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parents in the area are frustrated it never came to fruition.\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have to commute normally by car every morning, and then my son has to travel and take two different busses to come back home after school,\\\" Anne Maria said.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"score\": 0.9970402556192444, \"rank\": 0.0028983606728414085, \"text\": \"Maria\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hopefully there is something close by because just given how the daycares are run it's first come first serve,\\\" added Blake Meadows.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blake_Carrington\", \"score\": 0.7258354239452857, \"rank\": 0.37770709492801047, \"text\": \"Blake\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blake_Carrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blake_Carrington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2020, the BC NDP promised it would build the school in its campaign.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 967, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia_New_Democratic_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BC NDP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia_New_Democratic_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia_New_Democratic_Party\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No school has been approved or funded.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It takes a long time because it's a complex thing to build a school,\\\" said Brenda Bailey, NDP MLA for Vancouver-False Creek.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1142, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brenda_Bailey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brenda Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brenda_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brenda_Bailey\"}, {\"begin\": 1169, \"end\": 1190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver-False_Creek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vancouver-False Creek\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver-False_Creek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver-False_Creek\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For example, the negotiations between the City (of Vancouver) and the Vancouver School Board for that lease took quite a long time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 0.9999999489068627, \"rank\": 5.109316941729773e-08, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}, {\"begin\": 1264, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_School_Board\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vancouver School Board\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_School_Board\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_School_Board\"}, {\"begin\": 1264, \"end\": 1273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 0.9999999489068627, \"rank\": 5.109316941729773e-08, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Vancouver city councillor gave her thoughts on the matter.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 0.9999999489068627, \"rank\": 5.109316941729773e-08, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The land has been there for a long time.\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is been a lease in place and so it does seem a long time to get a new school in place, particularly in part of the city where we know there is a need,\\\" ABC Vancouver's Lisa Dominato said.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1590, \"end\": 1593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9870461026241493, \"rank\": 0.01312385011083089, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 0.9999999489068627, \"rank\": 5.109316941729773e-08, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], 